Comedian, actor and presenter Moshe Ndiki and his bae singer Phelo Bala are Mzansi’s  #CoupleGoals and recently got the stamp of approval from their moms. The couple have been flaunting their relationship on social media by posting loved up snaps with each other. They brought happiness to Mzansi this week when they posted a picture of their moms on social media and announced that they got blessings from both parents, proving that that love conquers all. Moshe wrote: “Above all else, Lord. Thank you for loving and supportive moms." Phelo is a private person and in the past been shy to speak on his personal life, but has been very open about his relationship with Moshe. It seems the couple are head over heels with each other. #LoveLivesHere.